Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The attacks by the Gundams\Nsent by the Space Colonies...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...reflected the colonies'\Nretaliatory intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.89,0:01:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ has masked its identity\Nin the Alliance Military...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.32,0:01:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the Gundams' mission\Nis to attack them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The year is After Colony 195.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ has finally taken\Ncenter stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,With an army of elite soldiers\Nat his command...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...Treize Khushrenada has begun\Nto wipe out the Alliance Military.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:02:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle between OZ and the\Nmobile suits sent to Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...causes serious repercussions\Non the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Explosive devices with\Ninfrared sensors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.50,0:02:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going after Treize!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Treize Khushrenada was using\Nus like a bunch of puppets...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We screwed up this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's go after Treize!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can still catch him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.23,0:03:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's not wise!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.20,0:03:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stay outta my way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Want me to shoot you?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Our tactics have always been\Na surprise attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But now the enemy\Nhas the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So we didn't get them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.26,0:03:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's get out of here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.03,0:03:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sure!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey kid! Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.94,0:04:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I ordered Lieutenant Zechs\Nto take control...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...of the Luxembourg\NHeadquarters...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...where they continue\Nto retaliate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He should be able to get\Nthings under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How shall we handle the\NGundams at New Edwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave that up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.36,0:04:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This base is completely\Nunder our control.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Request permission to head\Nfor New Edwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For New Edwards?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That won't be necessary.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just activate the missile{\i0}\N{\i1}self-detonation devices...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.57,0:05:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...at New Edwards.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-detonation devices?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure you can activate{\i0}\N{\i1}them from where you are.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then get to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's over-kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Demolishing an entire base\Njust to kill a few mobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Alliance Military couldn't\Ndo something this simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all this commotion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,An unusually large number\Nof aircraft are asking to land.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably the ones that escaped\Nfrom New Edwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too chaotic to be\Na mere Gundam attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Major Sally!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.81,0:05:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I've intercepted an\NOZ transmission!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna detonate the\Nmissiles at New Edwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:06:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trying to destroy\Nthe Gundams and the base!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We must land at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We can make a belly\Nlanding on the sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,System locked on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Preparing to activate{\i0}\N{\i1}detonation devices.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.51,0:06:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leave the premises.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I repeat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,These babies should get rid\Nof those Gundams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Your colleagues and injured\Nofficers are still there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd be glad to die\Nwith such honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take that as a compliment,\Nex-Alliance Forces Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.94,0:06:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Final safety device deactivated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.34,0:06:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}T-minus 900 to detonation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Major Sally, what are you\Ntrying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The system's locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing more you\Ncan do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing you try will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only 10 minutes\Nbefore the base is wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one person we couldn't\Neliminate if we wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A Gundam pilot I'm\Ninterested in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping I could\Nsee him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think this\Nwould happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit relying on us like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friend's just gone\Nthrough too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Heero!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know you can hear me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen to me, Heero!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So his name's Heero?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Detonation devices on the\Nbase's large missiles...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:07:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...were activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.07,0:08:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ is planning to blow\Nthe entire base apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...to kill you Gundams!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.78,0:08:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've confirmed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 47 large missiles\Nat the New Edwards Base...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...and if they were to\Nexplode at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...it'd instantly wipe out a\Nradius of about 300 kilometers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sticking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's less than 10 minutes\Nbefore the explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.36,0:08:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't get 300 kilometers\Naway in that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be able to cover\Nthat distance in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But please, grant me\Nmy one last wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Deactivate the missiles, Heero!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You coward, Heero!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You leaving us?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He isn't running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Missile base location confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Proceeding to enter base.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that, Heero.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stake my life on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A failed mission means death!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But my card isn't up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The detonation device{\i0}\N{\i1}has been activated...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.94,0:09:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...on the largest missile;\N{\i1}Model 304.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Model 304's explosion...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...will trigger the explosion{\i0}\N{\i1}of all the other missiles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hurry to the model 304{\i0}\N{\i1}control room.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in good shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've secured two carriers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The runway will be{\i0}\N{\i1}cleared soon!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hope we're not\Nwasting our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you get one more carrier\Nready for departure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Another one?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Heero's gonna need one too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.18,0:10:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His mobile suit's probably{\i0}\N{\i1}low on fuel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're totally confident\Nthat he's gonna succeed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.32,0:10:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to you now, Heero!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got a 10 percent\Nchance of succeeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But he can do it for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The detonation system\Nhasn't stopped yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.46,0:10:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Major Sally!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't believe anyone can\Nstop the explosion at that base!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would ever believe\Nsuch a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm proud of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna brag that I know Heero,\Nwho prevented the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to say you're\Nquite the guy, Heero!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a miserable mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I totally screwed up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I couldn't\Neliminate the Gundams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How were you planning\Nto destroy them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to activate the\Nself-detonation devices...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...of the New Edwards\Nbase missiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:12:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundams deactivated the\Nbombs and stopped the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Saved by the Gundams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Earth is a confined area.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't go around\Nthoughtlessly polluting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Human beings are weak\Nand vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody is capable of\Nkilling anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But we mustn't abuse\Nthis capability.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This time we'll have\Nto thank the Gundams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And Lady Une.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You must learn more\Nabout the OZ organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn about OZ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after all this damage there's\Nno sign of surrendering.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Brigadier-General Daigo\NOnegell's such a tenacious man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I hope he's also\Na hateful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise Zechs could feel\Nless resolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You expected the Alliance\NHeadquarters to fall so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting OZ come\None step closer to this base!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree that security at\Nthis base is splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But if your people were\Neven briefly careless...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...this base would be taken\Nover immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Zechs Merquise!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So you knew it was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You were cautious around\Nme during the Alliance days...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I thought you could\Ntell me apart from any others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the era!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.30,0:13:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The war made me do those things!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Annihilating the Sanc Kingdom\Nwasn't my personal desire...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...but the Alliance's decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.98,0:13:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sanc Kingdom had no\Nintention of resisting...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...against the Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But you staged an attack and\Ndestroyed the Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Many countries opposed the\Nexpanding military powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...of the United Earth\NSphere Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sanc Kingdom was\None of those opposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you could\Neliminate the revolt's cause...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...by destroying the\NRoyal family...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.53,0:13:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...since it influenced\Nneighboring countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You personally led the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Milliardo Peacecraft...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,May you rest in peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...the betrayed and outraged\NMilliardo Peacecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn about OZ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.81,0:14:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that I don't\Nunderstand Treize?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Two carriers from the 505\Nsupport troops...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...want to contact us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What type of carriers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Aries, from our own forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Big Nose;\Nbegin communication!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:14:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Which base did they\Ncome from?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,One moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The New Edwards base.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You fools! Those are enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.34,0:15:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The other carrier's headed\Nfor this Mother Ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm running out of fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This carrier wouldn't cause\Na big explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll leave on the\Nmobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A Gundam is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! On the ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight him with the Leos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty Leos have been destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.77,0:16:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw him into the sea\Nand get him with the Cancer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Treize's ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.17,0:16:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It left the fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It came out of the\Ncarrier that went down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.42,0:16:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam on the ship has\Ndestroyed the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,70% of our Leos have\Nbeen destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.69,0:16:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we use the Aries?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, all of our elevators\Nwill be targeted!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why now; on this happy day\Nof our new beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Colonel Une!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.47,0:16:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam's still attacking\Non the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you; throw him\Ninto the sea!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't inform me of\Nhis every move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.44,0:16:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just follow my orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:16:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam's now on the\Ntakeoff catapult line!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Send a Leo and shoot\Nthat Gundam into the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How are preparations?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,With this advanced mobility,\Nit should move like an Aries!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I can fly over\Nto the other Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That Gundam's attacking\NTreize's ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for much longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:18:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Destination reached!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go, Nataku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't be so sure of yourself,{\i0}\N{\i1}Gundam!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't get any\Ncloser to that ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody can stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't expecting this\Nmuch resistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's game-over now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid move, getting emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Step aside!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see for yourself\Nthat you'll never beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew Gundams\Nwere so powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Treize!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like your superior\Nwants to fight with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stop him in his tracks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Treize, it's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.47,0:19:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lady Une...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leave him to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Treize...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the real Treize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll gladly accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Wu Fei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Treize Khushrenada.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The duel is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a good fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me now or I'll\Ncome back until I get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.19,0:21:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we can battle again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.73,0:21:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.41,0:21:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Treize, how come you\Nlet that pilot escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the pilot of a mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.92,0:21:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it'd be fair to\Ngive him another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It was honorable to leave the\Nmobile suit and duel with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.66,0:21:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see why he makes\Nsuch a good Gundam pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.76,0:21:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time we'll fight with\Nhis specialty, the mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But Treize...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.01,0:22:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Did that guy actually\Naccomplish his mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.89,0:22:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.99,0:22:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.11,0:23:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The United Earth Sphere\NAlliance collapses...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the world heads down\Na path to chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero and Duo continue\Nto battle OZ...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.88,0:23:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...the reason behind the chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.92,0:23:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Zechs heads for the Sanc\NKingdom with his Tallgeese...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.85,0:23:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...to reclaim the homeland\Nof the Peacecrafts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.69,0:23:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But Tallgeese is an extremely\Ndangerous mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.23,0:23:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, on Gundam Wing, Episode 9,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.82,0:23:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,"Portrait of a Ruined Country".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.82,0:23:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,
